	<li id="menu-item-129702" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom current-menu-item menu-item-129702"><a href="https://www.truthdig.com/group/arts-and-culture/?bucket=td-originals" aria-current="page">Arts and Culture</a></li>
