        <h1 class="article-item__title ">
            The FBI Has a New Plan to Spy on High School Students Across the Country
        </h1>

        
                    <div class="layout layout--comment-share layout--comment-share-in-article">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container comment-share ">

            <div class="comment-share__social">
                <ul class="social-share  clearfix"><li class="social-share__item"><a class="social-share__icon social-share__icon--facebook " rel="nofollow" href="http://www.facebook.com/"
